name: Praecox: Supremum Sessionem
description:
CONTROLS:
[WASD] to move, [ESC] is the pause menu,
[Ctrl] crouch, [Left Shift] running,
[Space] Jumping and [Right Mouse] to zoom.

You will have to Alt+F4 out of the game (except in the start menu).

This game was made for LSD Jam 2022.

Walk around, just don't look at the clock, but you will hear it ticking. Look at things and find out where they take you.
There is the dream hotel and a small city. Currently, are three areas available.

CONTENT WARNING:
There are expressions of violence, drug use and strong language

Please don't expect more.
